 577:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         PWR_GPIO_BIT_0, ..., PWR_GPIO_BIT_15 (except for ports where less
 578:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         I/O pins are available) or the logical OR of several of them to set
 579:Drivers/STM32G0xx_HAL_Driver/Src/stm32g0xx_hal_pwr_ex.c ****   *         several bits for a given port in a single API call.
